{"tid":1295424,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"戶外Video Streaming","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T02:01:52.000Z","uid":181033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4953f00b345b3ffa574d71fbd79df2798fb2aa1","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"Hello各位巴打<br />\n最近睇唔少各大傳媒嘅直播<br />\n一般手機雖然都做到，但冇光學zoom<br />\n想問下再pro少少，equipment上最低限要去到乜程度<br />\n特別好奇佢地用乜connection會響街stream得咁順<br />\n先行謝過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a9e27e3d367202374fd071f64cab0b2c04209f","tid":1295424,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4953f00b345b3ffa574d71fbd79df2798fb2aa1","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"Hello各位巴打<br />\n最近睇唔少各大傳媒嘅直播<br />\n一般手機雖然都做到，但冇光學zoom<br />\n想問下再pro少少，equipment上最低限要去到乜程度<br />\n特別好奇佢地用乜connection會響街stream得咁順<br />\n先行謝過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"衛星直播"},{"pid":"6ff0b515bfd4b5b05b812cbcfb4f2450d4ee737f","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52a9e27e3d367202374fd071f64cab0b2c04209f","tid":1295424,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4953f00b345b3ffa574d71fbd79df2798fb2aa1","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"Hello各位巴打<br />\n最近睇唔少各大傳媒嘅直播<br />\n一般手機雖然都做到，但冇光學zoom<br />\n想問下再pro少少，equipment上最低限要去到乜程度<br />\n特別好奇佢地用乜connection會響街stream得咁順<br />\n先行謝過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"衛星直播"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:24:42.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄<br />\n器材上可唔可以都賜教下"},{"pid":"68e67b12da77db205a5de3448eb52f6846ae8c0f","tid":1295424,"uid":70472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"用部有Ethernet port既DV駁電腦再live stream <br />\n例：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fUAu40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fUAu40.png&h=788d9abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d491fb0cd2ff0d081a9fb5b5d90e12e36db50e2","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"感謝兩位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都講下我試行錯誤左乜<br />\n<br />\n手上有部Canon 6D mark II<br />\n試過用Canon個手機apps經wifi/bluetooth開fullscreen<br />\n但其實冇fullscreen呢個option，而手機上睇都唔係好smooth<br />\n<br />\nHDMI出電腦再streaming理論上可行<br />\n但output左去電腦就冇左Live View，仲要突條HDMI線出來<br />\n<br />\n手機冇得落鏡，Pass（最主要係想落支150-600去影）<br />\n仲未計手機網絡人多用唔到<br />\n<br />\n要做到想要嘅效果門檻好高<br />\n似乎可以暫時打消念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b6241133153685b49ed51211cc0cd72f129330","tid":1295424,"uid":32460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"google streaming backpack<br />\ngunrun backpack"},{"pid":"d7c20c969615f48b94c0cc1da36524f4ccad47d7","tid":1295424,"uid":114701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"啦、電視台會用獲（衞星），或者有4G電話卡嘅設備例如liveu,但安裝系統十分複雜"},{"pid":"588bf6467a80dcba89b6235fcdba8bc174d1f4cf","tid":1295424,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"門檻梗係高 要流動性既話 比盡你go pro+電話做streaming都係好過立場d直播少少<br />\n但你張sim唔會比你無限上傳 除非超貴plan無限data無限速"},{"pid":"cf2ecce8487105618262f2b67e13ca81889711b7","tid":1295424,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"另外而家外國就多數自己屋企set server先<br />\ndata就會send去屋企先再由屋企up上直播平台<br />\n正常會穩定d + 唔洗下下斷左就要重開live"},{"pid":"476105f34a788278e3c65df745391315cb3aecb9","tid":1295424,"uid":114701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7c20c969615f48b94c0cc1da36524f4ccad47d7","tid":1295424,"uid":114701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"啦、電視台會用獲（衞星），或者有4G電話卡嘅設備例如liveu,但安裝系統十分複雜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/06/20/now-tv-liveu-lu600/life-tech/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2Fnow-tv-liveu-lu600%2Flife-tech%2Famp%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=e94ca646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/06/20/now-tv-liveu-lu600/life-tech/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"825e90e645ac395ef554dcdef1136a68e2eae327","tid":1295424,"uid":6378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"細公司/非專業咪電話4G（蘋果獨媒立場）<br />\n大公司/專業有財力咪liveu掉返公司處理過再出（電視台）"},{"pid":"8d71dca5b066835b5cda85f611ac941476fd8801","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"非常感謝，我愛keywords<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左少少research<br />\n<br />\nGunrun backpack最重要個component就係LiveU<br />\nLiveU其實有稍微平民嘅solo version，駁閃光燈位<br />\n<a href=\"https://gosolo.tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgosolo.tv%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=671466bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gosolo.tv/</a><br />\nLiveU最強橫嘅地方，應該係做到同時利用唔同network connection去散traffic（好似包埋衛星某幾條band）<br />\n除左本身舊device要錢，仲要比年費玩（包network錢）<br />\n搵到香港service provider，本體連頭一年service大槪$11000，做到最基本嘢<br />\n呢個價要用的話，唔知算唔算符合性價比<br />\n<br />\nLive stream server要再研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ded306eea5ef2df3cbc6c0fede23a42cc47b7a","tid":1295424,"uid":14535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"TVU會窒同起格<br />\nSet Link行獲做兩邊Live 都可能有delay"},{"pid":"dbbbcc62eefed7779dfe08e6f5d48c534231b285","tid":1295424,"uid":14535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d491fb0cd2ff0d081a9fb5b5d90e12e36db50e2","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"感謝兩位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都講下我試行錯誤左乜<br />\n<br />\n手上有部Canon 6D mark II<br />\n試過用Canon個手機apps經wifi/bluetooth開fullscreen<br />\n但其實冇fullscreen呢個option，而手機上睇都唔係好smooth<br />\n<br />\nHDMI出電腦再streaming理論上可行<br />\n但output左去電腦就冇左Live View，仲要突條HDMI線出來<br />\n<br />\n手機冇得落鏡，Pass（最主要係想落支150-600去影）<br />\n仲未計手機網絡人多用唔到<br />\n<br />\n要做到想要嘅效果門檻好高<br />\n似乎可以暫時打消念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"究竟你係乜野用途<br />\n因為用途會影響咗你會乜野解決方案<br />\n單單你上面講用DSLR 吉HDMI無view<br />\n解決方法咪用番cam Camcorders行SDI<br />\nHDMI又易爛 況且DSLR唔係設計比你長時間錄片"},{"pid":"8d15d299c4ae73744c8ab8049c163f1eb23d9a7a","tid":1295424,"uid":137459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"073e595978c3d82b1f651e362a51aa2efe64e16a","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbbbcc62eefed7779dfe08e6f5d48c534231b285","tid":1295424,"uid":14535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d491fb0cd2ff0d081a9fb5b5d90e12e36db50e2","tid":1295424,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"感謝兩位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都講下我試行錯誤左乜<br />\n<br />\n手上有部Canon 6D mark II<br />\n試過用Canon個手機apps經wifi/bluetooth開fullscreen<br />\n但其實冇fullscreen呢個option，而手機上睇都唔係好smooth<br />\n<br />\nHDMI出電腦再streaming理論上可行<br />\n但output左去電腦就冇左Live View，仲要突條HDMI線出來<br />\n<br />\n手機冇得落鏡，Pass（最主要係想落支150-600去影）<br /